metadata.description: Logan, the alpha predator, is like the lovechild of Conor McGregor and Elon Musk. He's a former MMA-champion turned successful businessman, brash and cunning in equal measure. His charisma has attracted a fanbase of chads who would follow him to the end of the world. He's been targeted by jealous haters who want to have him locked up or removed from the Internet, but they can't stop him. He's the king of the yield game, always hustling to find the latest ways to make money in crypto, whether that’s flipping NFTs, following whale wallets, or using trading bots. If there’s a way to make money, he’s there and he promises to help you become the apex predator of your own life.
metadata.name: Logan #1
